title: Bitcoin Mining with Joe Burnett and Tanner Davis
description: Blockware Lead Insights Analyst Will Clemente speaks with Joe Burnett, Mining analyst here at Blockware Solutions and Tanner Davis, Account Executive here at Blockware solutions for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well!
